Feature: Dashboard — filters and sort

  Scenario Outline: dashboard <region>/<status>/<sort> #<i>
    Given I navigate to "/dashboard"
    Then "[data-testid=sales-table]" should be visible
    When I select "<region>" from "[data-testid=region-filter]"
    When I select "<status>" from "[data-testid=status-filter]"
    When I select "<sort>" from "[data-testid=sort-by]"
    Then "[data-testid=row-count]" should contain text "rows"
    Then "[data-testid=total-amount]" should contain text "$"

